{"tid":2421333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[最強對決] 係中國歷史上，邊個皇帝最接近川普？","createTime":"2021-02-24T12:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T09:06:08.000Z","uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8e865032b5272347bd71206d42df5d49420f81","tid":2421333,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"川普係美國開國以來最強既總統<br />\n呢點係美國人公認既不爭事實<br />\n如果將川普放係中國<br />\n係2300年歷史上，邊個皇帝可以及得上佢？<br />\n<br />\n係千古一帝 開天闢地既贏政？<br />\n文韜武略 四夷朝服既漢武帝？<br />\n南征北伐 亂世奸雄既魏武帝？<br />\n文武雙全 開創盛世既唐太宗？<br />\n革新開放 仁愛寬厚既宋太祖？<br />\n定係野心勃勃 探索世界既明成祖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過係古今中外 都好難搵到一個可以同川普雙提並論既統治者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>我川威武 拜登吃屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"67477eb596734024124de7a1d1a7fe25e1e74bd1","tid":2421333,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"我個人認為啦<br />\n川普內政能力堪比漢文帝<br />\n性格可類西楚霸王項羽<br />\n對外既強勢領導 比較似大清聖祖康熙大帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327c294dc6f1e81e81f47e6fd3038ab0e1133138","tid":2421333,"uid":23445,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"林鄭太祖"},{"pid":"8b79f21d1aa9fefa6b61b69586260ca992b2595a","tid":2421333,"uid":201031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:35:32.000Z","msg":"習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"